Absorption enhancement, Π(λ), is defined as the ratio of power absorbed in the Si layer of the cell with graphene nanoribbon (Ag nanostrip) to that of bare cell. Bare cells do not possess any graphene nanoribbon. Therefore, the absorption enhancement is given by:
